parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or death to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Warning lights on the display indicate a malfunction of the airbag system
corrosion on the left front sensor
failure of airbags to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delayed or unresponsive recall repair can leave vehicles with safety-critical issues on the road, putting drivers and passengers at risk.
symptoms: Dealerships fail to schedule recall repairs
parts are ordered but not received
lack of communication from dealerships
recall repairs are not completed despite multiple attempts to schedule.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden acceleration can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without warning
accelerates when braking
accelerates when removing foot from the accelerator pedal and placing it on the brake pedal
accelerates independently
and crashes into objects without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause a loss of power steering assist, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel tightens or locks up
the power steering indicator light comes on
the vehicle veers to one side while driving
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS bushing/damper can cause the power steering motor to vibrate on the steering column, leading to a slow leak of hydraulic power steering fluid, altering the alignment, and causing a loss of power steering assist.
symptoms: A popping or clunking sound in the steering column
the steering wheel shakes or pulls to one side
especially at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear hub bushings can cause abnormal tire wear, noise, and vibration, leading to reduced vehicle stability and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Noise in the rear of the vehicle
abnormal tire wear
vibration
and reduced vehicle stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The problems with the front and rear suspension can cause reduced vehicle stability, abnormal tire wear, and noise, leading to increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Abnormal tire wear
noise
vibration
and reduced vehicle stability
especially when driving on straight roads
curves
and during braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning evaporator can cause aluminum dust to be released into the cabin, potentially harming the health of occupants.
symptoms: Dust or debris coming from the air vents
reduced airflow from the vents
musty or unpleasant odor from the vents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially harm occupants.
symptoms: Sudden loud noise
shattered sunroof glass
damage to the roof or surrounding areas.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rodent Infestation through Air Filtration System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design flaw in the air filtration system allows rodents to gain access to the interior cabin, potentially carrying diseases and causing damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Evidence of rodent infestation
such as droppings or gnaw marks
musty or unpleasant odor
rodents seen or trapped inside the vehicle.
